description: Try our easy to follow Spaghetti With Chicken Tomato & Pesto recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Pasta,Seafood free,Low salt,Low sugar,Sesame free,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,Soy free,Quick & easy lunch,Tomato,Chicken
name: Spaghetti With Chicken Tomato & Pesto Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500g skinless chicken breast fillets (cut into bite sized pieces)

recipeInstructions.text: Place the pasta into a large pot of salted boiling water and cook according to packet instructions.
Meanwhile, place the olive oil in a large frying pan over a medium high heat. Add the chicken and cook for 5 minutes or until it colours.
Reduce the heat to medium, add the butter and garlic and cook until fragrant. Add the tomatoes and cook for a minute or so, or until they start to soften and the chicken is cooked through.
Drain the pasta, reserving 1/4 cup of the starchy water. Place the pasta in the frying pan with the buttery chicken, then add the pesto and rocket leaves.
Add a splash of the reserved cooking water, stir well and serve.
